<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><code>pwd</code> from the Terminal to display the working directory</li>
<li aria-level="1"><code>open .</code> opens a Finder window with the current directory from the Terminal</li>
<li aria-level="1"><code>cd</code> brings you to your default directory (on macOS, that’s usually your home folder)</li>
